dc_title_s: Profile of the lakes and Atlantic waterways via the Great Lakes and connecting rivers: the St. Lawrence River and the Champlain--Hudson Valley from Chicago and Duluth--Superior to New York and Quebec
dc_description_s: Prepared by the Engineering Department of the Sanitary District of Chicago. |Blueprint. Printed on 2 sheets, joined. Signed "Dr. James B. Angell, compliments of L. Cooley."
